project_descr: The PalTel Group Foundation will provide support to the procurement of medical supplies (drugs and health consumables) to the Ministry of Health in Gaza.

donor_name: The paltel group Foundation is an independent, non-profit organization established by the Paltel Group in 2008 as a  direct response to the growing needs of Palestinian society.
outputs.output_descr: UNDP/PAPP will procure drugs and health consumables for delivery to the Ministry of Health in Gaza
